{
  "stem": "1132.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944 into 1945-- what exactly was it like in hiding?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anything that you can remember that you haven't already said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, what do I remember?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember air raids, lots of air raids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember-- when we were hiding in the second apartment house, I remember not going out on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were, I would say, good couple of months-- two to three months-- where I wasn't out on the street at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because at that point, A, we were hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "B, it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was fighting on the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Hungarian soldiers, the Germans, and the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Russians were zeroing in on and really advancing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were hearing the gunfights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were hearing the air raids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were hearing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things that were extremely scary, especially scary for a young kid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Memories of being scared also are very vivid, because my father wasn't always around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As I said earlier, he was coming and going and keeping ahead of them, because he knew he was an able-bodied man.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if anybody finds him, he'll be taken immediately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whether it was too late to be taken to the camps, at that point-- which I think it was-- or whether he was going to be just plain shot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We also knew that as time was running out on the Germans, they were trying to just shoot people on the streets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And not--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is late '44, early '45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the time frame here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things were really getting very tight for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, there were parts of Europe already liberated at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
